{
  "texts": [
    "On examination, visual acuity was 20/20 in the right eye and 20/20 in the left eye.",
    "There was no relative afferent pupillary defect.",
    "Extraocular motility was full.",
    "IOP was 23 mmHg in the right eye and 17 mmHg in the left eye.",
    "She correctly identified 13/13 Ishihara color plates with the right and left eyes."
  ]
